    "Thus, it is important to properly clean data before using it for training the models.",
    "Overfitting is also common within AI models used in genome analysis due to the limited availability of data.",
    "This is further restricted by confidentiality issues.",
    "Nevertheless, it is recommended to have even more stringent rules and regulations to protect the data of patients.",
    "Another disadvantage of using AI in genome analysis is that the model needs to be reoptimized based on the population under study."
